# bOS — Windsurf Rules

You are working on bOS, a personal operating system with 17 AI agents and 47 skills.

Read `AGENTS.md` for full architecture overview.

## Quick Reference
- Agents: `.claude/agents/*.md` (17 agents)
- Skills: `.claude/skills/*/SKILL.md` (47 skills, YAML frontmatter + Markdown)
- User profile: `profile.md` (DO NOT auto-modify)
- User state: `state/*.md` (DO NOT auto-modify)
- System config: `CLAUDE.md` (full spec), `AGENTS.md` (cross-platform brief)
- Schemas: `state/SCHEMAS.md`
- Database: `supabase/*.sql`

## Conventions
- Skills have YAML frontmatter: `name`, `description`, `user_invocable`, `command`
- State files: Summary (first ~25 lines) + Active section + Archive
- Language: match the user's language from profile.md
- Every response ends with a concrete next step
- Never store secrets in files — use /vault skill
